Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,來翔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.38,0:02:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,始 始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.18,0:02:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,笨蛋 看上面
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.47,0:03:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,休想 嵐空
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,聖絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.27,0:03:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,希婭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.02,0:03:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.71,0:03:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,現在如果走出我的防護圈 你也會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.22,0:03:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不枉我在這裡埋伏多時
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.64,0:04:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,的確不容小視 你們實在太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.73,0:04:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,尤其是那個男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,受到我的烏拉諾司吐息正面攻擊居然還沒死
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.73,0:04:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你們究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.04,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,究竟學會了多少神代魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,提問之前 不會先自報名號嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.58,0:04:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,魔人族都是些不知禮儀的粗人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.38,0:04:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,沒事吧 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.24,0:04:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,對一個將死之人 沒必要自報名號了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.09,0:04:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是照慣例問一句
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.20,0:05:02.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我對你不感興趣 你也不用多想
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,話說回來 你同伴的手臂傷勢如何
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,比以前帥多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.98,0:05:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫弗利德·巴古亞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.64,0:05:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我為異教徒降下神罰 是忠實的神之使徒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.47,0:05:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,神之使徒是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.18,0:05:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,獲得了神代魔法 所以膽敢如此自詡是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,挺聰明
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.67,0:05:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我獲得神代之力的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.78,0:05:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那位大人親口對我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.24,0:05:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我的使徒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.49,0:05:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我將獻上我的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,完成那位大人的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,你們的存在就是障礙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要全力將你們否定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我的台詞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,擋在我面前的你就是我的敵人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,敵人殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.00,0:06:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不會以為我帶來的魔物只有龍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.42,0:06:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,想破壞這屏障可沒那麼容易
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.42,0:06:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,讓你們見識一下 我所獲得的神代之力
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.31,0:06:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,登峰造極 上天入地
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.76,0:06:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而吾等難以企及 徒留南柯一夢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}不如賜予斷絕 將無限世界劃開空隙
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.71,0:06:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,穿破境界 創造神域迴廊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.38,0:06:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,回聖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.64,0:07:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,後面 始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.87,0:07:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,為什麼會有這種錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明主人也只是個普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.31,0:07:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,會受傷 也會因為一時疏忽而喪命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那麼妾身 妾身該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.16,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,活下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,父親大人 可是我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.13,0:07:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,從今以後 龍人族不得出現在世人面前
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,龍人族的倖存者是神敵 一旦被人發現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.11,0:08:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,獵龍就會開始 那我們就真的要滅絕了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.69,0:08:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,這道理不言自明
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.89,0:08:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,只能永遠躲著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.33,0:08:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,不 總會有時機成熟的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.87,0:08:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,拋棄仁義之時 吾等即與鳥獸無異
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.47,0:08:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,唯有理性之劍緊握在手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.93,0:08:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,吾等永為龍人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,這是什麼威力
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.20,0:08:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,再這麼下去要撐不住了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.47,0:08:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,去你媽的吧 極限突破
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.29,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,十字浮游炮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.18,0:09:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼會如此頑強
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,明明差點就要了他的命
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.82,0:09:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,最後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.82,0:09:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,怎…怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.53,0:09:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,是黑龍？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,龍…龍人族不是已經滅絕了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.11,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,休想再傷害主人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.27,0:10:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,年輕人 記好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,此乃真·龍之吐息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.96,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,沒想到能在這種地方見到龍人族的倖存者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.58,0:10:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,沒辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然很危險
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.16,0:10:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,也只能用魔法把這整個空間…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.76,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,想得美
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.04,0:11:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 時間到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.36,0:11:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 振作點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.24,0:11:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怖的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,他身邊的幾個女人也非同一般
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.49,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,有本以為已經滅絕的龍人族
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.60,0:11:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,還有無詠唱無法陣的魔法使
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,以及似乎能預知未來的大力兔人族
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.87,0:12:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕用上神代之力 竟也落得如此境地
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.09,0:12:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,如果最開始那次攻擊沒能命中他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.11,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,被大卸八塊的人就是我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,怎麼說得好像你已經贏了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.33,0:12:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我還能繼續打呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.11,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我想也是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你的殺意如同奔流湧動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.91,0:12:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,即使身負重傷也絲毫不減
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.20,0:12:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,令人恐懼的不僅是你的戰鬥力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.40,0:12:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,還有將敵人趕盡殺絕的殺意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:43.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不對 是對生存的執念
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,本來我也不想用這招
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,但為了殺掉你這種強敵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.49,0:12:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這也是必須付出的代價吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.47,0:12:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你在胡扯些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人 岩漿上漲了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.82,0:13:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.98,0:13:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是破壞了拱心石
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.82,0:13:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,拱心石？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,看著這些岩漿你們不覺得奇怪嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.18,0:13:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,古盧恩大火山很明顯是活火山
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.87,0:13:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 從未有過火山噴發的紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.47,0:13:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,有東西控制著地下岩漿的噴發
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.78,0:13:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.47,0:14:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,如你們所願
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,與大迷宮一起埋葬在此地吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.96,0:14:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,始
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,始大人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.87,0:14:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 你聽著
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.78,0:14:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你帶著這個從上面逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,妾身…唯獨妾身不值得與諸位共赴黃泉嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.58,0:14:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒時間了我只說一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我可沒認命
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:14:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我會獲得神代魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,總有一天我也會宰了那混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.80,0:14:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我會守約把靜因石帶回安卡吉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,但是 我一個人辦不到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.33,0:15:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我想請你幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.18,0:15:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,除了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,沒人能突破重圍 儘快回到安卡吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.78,0:15:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了 緹奧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.60,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.49,0:15:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,緹奧 替我向香織和繆說一聲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.42,0:15:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,「待會再見」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.11,0:16:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,這點小傷 反而更讓人興奮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.33,0:16:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,直接來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.00,0:16:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.91,0:16:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,痛覺變換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.87,0:16:37.09,Default,,0,0,0,,承受的傷痛越多 所有屬性值越上漲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.62,0:16:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,這都要怪始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.78,0:16:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,正好 我喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.36,0:16:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哦 爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.80,0:17:02.02,Default,,0,0,0,,主人 愛死你了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,居然能從那種地方逃出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.82,0:17:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,一群怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,然而就算你是黑龍 也已經滿身瘡痍
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.87,0:17:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我來送你歸西…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.09,0:17:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你們 主人 月 希婭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.67,0:17:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,古盧恩大火山噴發了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.78,0:18:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,父王 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,您要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.49,0:18:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,父王
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.62,0:18:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,原來你在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,疾馳 風爪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.02,0:19:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你是從哪來的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.36,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,是哪位貴族的寵物貓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.51,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,從主人身邊逃走了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.36,0:19:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,真可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.36,0:19:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喵 真可愛喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.16,0:19:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,但是居然離家出走 真是個壞孩子喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.56,0:19:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就讓小喵雫來懲罰你這個壞孩子喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 你要去哪喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.87,0:19:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,苗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.02,0:19:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,發現你沒陪著光輝同學
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.93,0:19:50.91,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我來找你了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.71,0:20:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,別看我 殺了我吧喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,然後呢 王宮和教會怎麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 要儘早讓光輝同學們擁有對抗魔人族的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.13,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,說的都是這些話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.44,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,關於南雲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,雖然還沒確定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.91,0:20:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,莉莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.73,0:20:29.13,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他們有提到認定南雲同學為異端分子
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,不像是開玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.49,0:20:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.49,0:20:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什麼鬼 開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.44,0:20:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,可惡 為什麼他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.33,0:20:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,脾氣還挺大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.06,0:20:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,這也沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.22,0:20:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,畢竟心愛的公主大人 眼睜睜被人奪走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.91,0:21:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,你滾 他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.89,0:21:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我已經沒理由繼續跟著你了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.73,0:21:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想要嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.93,0:21:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,既然被搶走了 那就再搶回來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.51,0:21:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.44,0:21:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,就算他還活著
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.31,0:21:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你動手殺他的事實也無法抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫殺人未遂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,當然我也不想告發同班同學
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.27,0:21:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,你還想威脅我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我也沒說讓你對我言聽計從
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.07,0:21:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,只要一如既往 我們各自追求想要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.96,0:21:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,這叫互利互惠
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.60,0:21:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 差不多該收場了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,到時候 你的願望就能實現了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.89,0:21:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.04,0:21:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.07,0:23:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 親子再會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:50.70,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Tears streaming down your sorrow face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:56.70,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Came a long and painful road, you gave yourself away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:01:02.04,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You saw everything, heaven to hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.33,0:01:08.46,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You say you need a self redemption, to mend the broken wings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.96,0:01:13.89,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Drowning in the dark, no place to be
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.59,0:01:17.64,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}But I am by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:19.47,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}You’re not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.73,0:01:25.40,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, shed a light so you won’t disappear
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:31.36,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Cause I know where you belong, save your saddened heart
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.36,0:01:37.08,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}With a flashback, screaming out but still we’re holding on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.24,0:01:42.50,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Waiting for the break of dawn for a new day to begin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.96,0:01:45.75,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Daylight, daylight
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.34,0:01:51.09,OP-EN,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.8}Stay a little while longer
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}全部　期待してみて幻だった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}信じたかった　縋りたかった
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}身体の底に開いた螺旋状の穴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}ボクだけじゃなく　キミにもなんだね
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}許されることなど　もう望んじゃいない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}抱き寄せてもまた　わからないシルエット
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}躊躇いもなく傷つけた代償か
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}キミの側は　揺れてボクを離れた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}道を違える度に　ボクの後ろに穴が開く
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}伸びた一本の影
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}誰もが手にし得る　小さな欠片で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何ができる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}どちらが欲しいかなんて　残酷な問い神様は
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}何度ボクらに投げかける
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.77,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}期待的一切皆為虛空一場
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.77,0:22:17.27,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}破滅的希望　虛偽的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.19,0:22:23.99,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嵌入身體的傷口深不見底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:29.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不僅是我　你也背負同樣的傷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:38.34,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}早已不再奢望　求得誰人原諒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.34,0:22:42.88,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哪怕懷中相擁　徒留輪廓難辨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.88,0:22:47.43,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}甘願承傷不曾猶豫的代價
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:52.56,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我步履蹣跚　忍痛離開你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.56,0:22:57.52,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.52,0:23:02.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:07.11,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}幾步對錯　令我身負百孔千瘡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.11,0:23:10.16,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}形單影隻漸行漸遠
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.45,0:23:16.62,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望碎片　誰人不曾擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.87,0:23:21.21,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}又能作何掙扎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.21,0:23:26.38,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}神明凜然在上　拋下兩難抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.38,0:23:31.22,ED-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不斷拷問你我
